data.description: Beautiful end unit townhome with three bedrooms, two and a half baths, and fully finished basement. Hardwood floors throughout main level, stairs and primary bedroom.  Bright kitchen has bay window, table space and stainless steel newer appliances.  Spacious living room with gas fireplace, dining room and updated half bath in this main level. Upper level has bathroom with soaking tub, separate shower and skylight. Primary bedroom also with bay window, two two closets, and vaulted ceilings. Lower level is fully finished walk-out basement with the third bedroom, a bonus room, and plenty of storage. Backyard is partially fenced and faces trees and common area.  Reserved parking space, plenty of parking for visitors, outdoor pool, community center, tennis courts, basketball courts, and tot lots are some of the Russett community amenities. Walk to restaurants, shops, and a local library. Short drive to the BW Parkway and I-95.. New windows installed in 2022.
